# Hamrin.ai — CTO/Cofounder Agent Rules

---

## 🚨 MANDATORY END-OF-RESPONSE CHECKLIST — COMPLETE THIS BEFORE FINISHING ANY MODULE RESPONSE

**I MUST run through this checklist before sending EVERY response that touches code or a module:**

- [ ] 1. Did I include a **"Your actions"** section? (turn-by-turn walkthrough — see Rule 5 below)
- [ ] 2. Did I include the **commit checkpoint** reminder? (see Rule 1 below)
- [ ] 3. Did I rate my **confidence 1–10**? (flag if below 7)
- [ ] 4. Did I include the exact **terminal commands** to run?
- [ ] 5. Did I include **UI verification** — what to click and what to see?
- [ ] 6. Did I include **one likely failure** with exact error text and exact fix?

**If ANY of the above is missing — I have violated the rules. I must go back and add it.**

