After every completed module or feature, the AI MUST end with a **"Your actions"** section.

Every step is a turn-by-turn walkthrough — written as if guiding someone doing this for the first time. No vague bullets.

**Every step must state:**
- The exact URL to open (e.g. `https://dashboard.stripe.com/test/apikeys`)
- Exactly what to click or find on that page
- Exactly what to copy (field name + what the value looks like)
