- Exactly what terminal command to run

**Required sections in every "Your actions":**
1. **Env vars** — exact URL → what to click → what to copy → open exact file → paste at exact line
2. **Terminal commands** — listed in order, one per line, copy-pasteable
3. **UI verification** — exactly what to click and exactly what you should see when it works
4. **One likely failure** — the exact error text, and the exact fix (which file, which line, what to change to what)

**Example format:**
> Step 1: Go to https://dashboard.stripe.com/test/apikeys
> Click "Reveal test key" next to "Secret key"
> Copy the value — it starts with `sk_test_`
>
